title: Fleetcare

creator: Next Generation Mobility GmbH
descriptionHtml:
The Fleetcare App is now available!

The App enables users to book and interact with vehicles during a trip.
Simple and Intuitive Design adds up, to offer the best user experience and save you time, just like the Fleetcare Web App.

Fleetcare is a web-based software, that helps companies have control of their Fleets, reduce mobility costs, simplify the process to book company vehicles through automatic bookings and key management, integrate and optimize the usage of electric vehicles, and motivate employees with private bookings.

Our software has uncountable functions:
- Booking Platform
- Vehicle Management
- Calendar Integration
- Key Management
- Driver Log
- Driver License Control
- Data Export
- Analytics
- Keyless Access to Vehicles
- And many more features to come related to Vehicle usage, CO2 Tracking, CO2 Optimization, etc.

We are proud to have you use our App, and with it, be always updated on your bookings, anywhere.

With this app you have the following features:
- Control your own bookings
- Book Business or Private trips.
- Keyless access to vehicles that have our hardware integrated.
- Assistance for other key management methods.
descriptionShort: The App enables users to book and interact with vehicles during a trip.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
- Added ability to require mandatory RFID scan prior to booking release
- Improved Geotab integration in the vehicle selection process
- UX improvements in the ongoing booking screen

Our software has uncountable functions:
- Booking Platform
- Vehicle Management
- Calendar Integration
- Key Management
- Driver Log
- Driver License Control
- Data Export
- Analytics
- Keyless Access to Vehicles
- And many more features to come related to Vehicle usage, CO2 Tracking, CO2 Optimization, etc.

We are proud to have you use our App, and with it, be always updated on your bookings, anywhere.

With this app you have the following features:
- Control your own bookings
- Book Business or Private trips.
- Keyless access to vehicles that have our hardware integrated.
- Assistance for other key management methods.
